{"tid":1848369,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢工作的人回到家鄉，被老家人用木板釘死在屋內隔離起來","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T12:36:28.000Z","uid":37204,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae6f8fc716c363512cfb09fe117289d0de66eae","tid":1848369,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"【新唐人北京時間2020年01月28日訊】武漢新型肺炎疫情急劇擴散，武漢人在外省遭遇全面圍攻。日前，有網民曝光，在武漢工作的人返回到家鄉，家門被民眾用木條釘死，人卻被隔離在屋內。<br />\n<br />\n網民「財經冷眼@charles984681」1月27日在推特发文表示，「武漢工作的人回到家鄉，被老家人用木板釘死在屋內隔離起來！當人性的惡被激發，便專挑弱者下狠手！這是一場文革式的沒有人性的瘟疫，比武漢肺炎更可怕。」<br />\n<br />\n推文配發的一條視頻顯示，至少有5人圍在一戶人家門前，用多塊木板將房門釘死。雖然屋內的人在不斷交涉，但仍然擋不住門外鐵鎯頭的敲擊聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1221830671343087616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1221830671343087616&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=057332ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1221830671343087616&h=23d317fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1221830671343087616</a><br />\n<br />\n轉自PTT<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pttweb.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1580208621.A.B8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pttweb.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1580208621.A.B8F&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=a859c03d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pttweb.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1580208621.A.B8F</a>"},{"pid":"f0daed2adc440b80af9c96bacefab090b9ee8119","tid":1848369,"uid":167295,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"十四天隔離期後，武漢人證實沒有患上肺炎，卻被活生生的餓死了。"},{"pid":"b1c6addcb79a124ff9377095392c9a01cb441680","tid":1848369,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"現代耶穌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i